OL,7,FA public schoolboy who attacked two
OL,8,Fsleeping students and a teacher with
OL,9,Fhammers at Blundell's School in
OL,10,FTiverton, Devon, has been found guilty
OL,11,Fof three counts attempted murder at
OL,12,FExeter Crown Court.
OL,14,FA 17-year-old has been found guilty on
OL,15,Fthree counts of attempted murder in
OL,16,Fconnection to an incident at a
OL,17,Fboarding school in Devon.
