OL,7,FThe teenager, who was 16 at the time
OL,8,Fand cannot be named for legal reasons,
OL,9,Fwas on trial after attacking two
OL,10,Fsleeping students and a teacher at
OL,11,FBlundell's School in Tiverton.
OL,13,FReturning on Friday 21 June, the jury
OL,14,Ffound the defendant guilty of three
OL,15,Fcounts of attempted murder after 40
OL,16,Fhours of deliberation.
