OL,7,FDuring the two-month trial, Exeter
OL,8,FCrown Court heard the boy was wearing
OL,9,Fjust his boxer shorts and was "on a
OL,10,Fmission" to protect himself from a
OL,11,Fzombie apocalypse when he carried out
OL,12,Fthe attack on 9 June last year.
OL,14,FThe teenager claimed he was
OL,15,Fsleepwalking when he seriously injured
OL,16,Fthe two boys and left housemaster
OL,17,FHenry Roffe-Silvester with wounds to
OL,18,Fhis head.
