OL,7,FOver Christmas or in the spring term
OL,8,Fhe sent him "unkind" messages, the boy
OL,9,Ftold police.
OL,11,F"One I can remember... he said,
OL,12,F'F***ing die'," the boy said.
OL,14,F"I said to him not to say that because
OL,15,Fit is not very nice. There was a
OL,16,Fcomplete change during the summer
OL,17,Fholidays because before that he was
OL,18,Fnice."
