OL,7,FTrial judge Mrs Justice Cutts said she
OL,8,Fwould adjourn sentencing for the
OL,9,Fpreparation of pre-sentence reports,
OL,10,Fincluding a psychiatric report, and
OL,11,Fwould pass sentence on 18 October.
OL,13,F"I don't intend to sentence today,
OL,14,Ffurther reports are needed," she said.
OL,16,F"I would wish a psychiatric report.
OL,17,FThat needs to be a court-ordered
OL,18,Freport.
