OL,7,FFollowing the verdict, Blundell's
OL,8,Fheadteacher Bart Wielenga sent a
OL,9,Fletter to the school community.
OL,11,FHe wrote: "The trial ended today with
OL,12,FGuilty verdicts on all three counts of
OL,13,Fattempted murder and I wanted to write
OL,14,Fto you with our immediate response.
OL,16,F"It concludes a challenging year and I
OL,17,Fhope that this outcome will bring a
OL,18,Fdegree of closure for all those
OL,19,Finvolved.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/21
