OL,3,CSchoolboy who attacked pupils and
OL,4,Cteacher found guilty of attempted
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"The trial highlighted the remarkable
OL,8,Factions of the boys in (the house). I
OL,9,Falso want to commend Mr. and Mrs.
OL,10,FRoffe-Silvester not only for their
OL,11,Factions on the night of the incident
OL,12,Fbut also for their ongoing leadership
OL,13,Fin the ensuing months.
OL,15,F"Their efforts, and those of several
OL,16,Fsenior pupils, combined with the swift
OL,17,Fresponse of the emergency services and
OL,18,Fthe exceptional skill of the surgeons,
OL,19,Fundoubtedly saved the boys' lives.
