OL,7,F"You may have read the press reports
OL,8,Fon the trial referring to weapons and
OL,9,Flocked drawers. I want to reiterate
OL,10,Fthat they were tools and not weapons
OL,11,F(many items could be used as weapons)
OL,12,Fand that locked drawers are part of
OL,13,Fthe 'National Minimum Standards that
OL,14,Fboarding schools must meet in order to
OL,15,Fsafeguard and protect children in
OL,16,Ftheir care'.
OL,18,F"It is a regulatory requirement to
OL,19,Fgive pupils a lockable facility.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/21
