OL,7,F"We continue to be thankful for the
OL,8,Fremarkable recovery made by all the
OL,9,Fvictims and those affected by the
OL,10,Fevent.
OL,12,F"We are mindful that the psychological
OL,13,Fwounds sometimes take longer to heal
OL,14,Fthan the physical ones, and we will
OL,15,Fcontinue to exercise vigilance and
OL,16,Fcare in supporting all the staff and
OL,17,Fpupils directly or indirectly involved.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/21
