OL,7,F"I have stressed to pupils in numerous
OL,8,Fassemblies over the past year that
OL,9,Fthis incident is not something that we
OL,10,Fare ashamed of. It is part of our
OL,11,Fshared story.
OL,13,F"Difficult things happen in life, and
OL,14,Fwe want to teach young people that we
OL,15,Fcan talk openly about our fears and
OL,16,Fanxieties as they relate to difficult
OL,17,Fevents in life.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/21
