OL,7,F"We will continue to foster a
OL,8,Fsensitive, balanced, honest, and
OL,9,Fcourageous response to this tragic
OL,10,Fevent."
OL,12,FDevon and Cornwall Police also
OL,13,Fresponded to the verdict.
OL,15,FSenior Investigating Officer detective
OL,16,Finspector Dave Egan said: "We welcome
OL,17,Ftoday's verdict. This was an
OL,18,Funprovoked attack on two schoolboys as
OL,19,Fthey slept in their beds.
